     C                     MOVE 'Y'       WOKFL                           CIR005
     C                     Z-ADDWZDAYN    WPDAT                           CIR005
     C                     ELSE                                           CIR005
     C                     MOVE 'N'       WERR                            CIR005
     C                     ENDIF                                          CIR005
     C                     ENDIF                                          CIR005
      *                                                                   CIR005
      ** Endif for CIR005 = Y.                                            CIR005
      *                                                                   CIR005
     C                     ENDIF                                          CIR005
     C                     END
     C*
     C**  Confirmed holiday ind. must be 'Y' if date is a holiday, else *BLANK
